{"tid":1676341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"惡法已撤回 四大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-10-26T11:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:15:06.000Z","uid":61015,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa7c19fbdfb4ac795d7f35bb31daebd2f692b1c","tid":1676341,"uid":61015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"四你老母呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n點解依然仲係五大訴求？<br />\n<br />\n因為最重要嘅真正普選 一人一票選特首 <br />\n<br />\n什麼撤回條例 什麼成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都只係開俾市民嘅空頭支票 <br />\n<br />\n因為而家佢哋只係需要向共產黨交代<br />\n<br />\n香港達唔到真正嘅自治 政府就唔會做到以民為本<br />\n<br />\n我哋只會一步一步咁比共產黨蠶食香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續用大家嘅方法同你識嘅 唔識嘅人講出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>五大訴求 缺一不可</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f7c0d066c1cf8f081d469e5e44c381e69d32815","tid":1676341,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"自己作四大訴求去屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ad77f9cbae740ac3c23d7f05ee26f04e92a5a9","tid":1676341,"uid":286564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">立刻解散黑警，重建守護香港人民的警隊。</span></span></strong>"}]}